OL,3,CUK firms splash out almost #236,000 in
OL,4,Cpast year on AI, poll finds
OL,6,FBritish businesses spent nearly
OL,7,F#236,000 each on artificial
OL,8,Fintelligence (AI) in the past year as
OL,9,Fthey look to get ahead in the race to
OL,10,Fembrace the new technology, according
OL,11,Fto a report.
OL,13,FThe latest Barclays Business
OL,14,FProsperity index survey found that
OL,15,Flarge corporates with more than 250
OL,16,Fworkers invested the most ` at an
OL,17,Faverage of #400,000 on AI and emerging
OL,18,Ftechnologies over the past 12 months `
OL,19,Fcompared with #225,500 from medium
OL,20,Ffirms and #125,250 from small
OL,21,Fcompanies.
