OL,3,CUK firms splash out almost #236,000 in
OL,4,Cpast year on AI, poll finds
OL,6,FMore than two thirds ` 68% ` of all
OL,7,Fbusinesses are also looking to
OL,8,Fincrease this spend in the coming year
OL,9,Fas the AI revolution shows no sign of
OL,10,Fslowing.
OL,12,FThe poll of 1,000 decision makers at
OL,13,Ffirms found that almost nine in 10
OL,14,Fcompanies are turning to AI to solve
OL,15,Fkey business issues, such as energy
OL,16,Fcosts and infrastructure ` with 32%
OL,17,Fhaving already hired or currently
OL,18,Fhiring for AI-focused roles and 42%
OL,19,Fplanning to do so.
