OL,3,CUK firms splash out almost #236,000 in
OL,4,Cpast year on AI, poll finds
OL,6,FAway from AI, firms are generally
OL,7,Fplanning to ramp up investment by 5.5%
OL,8,Fin the next year, which is up from
OL,9,F3.8% in the first quarter, on areas
OL,10,Fsuch as staff training and
OL,11,Fdevelopment, digital offerings and
OL,12,Fresearch and development (R&D).
OL,14,FBut over half of firms surveyed (55%)
OL,15,Fin a separate poll by Barclays last
OL,16,Fmonth said they are delaying
OL,17,Finvestment decisions until after the
OL,18,Fautumn Budget, which has now been
OL,19,Fconfirmed for November 26.
